icture, each followed by an extensive Q&A with the director. Also featured are exclusive interviews and commentary with many cast members and collaborators, and members of legendary rock group, The Doors. Films covered include Johnny Suede, Living In Oblivion, Box of Moonlight, The Real Blonde, Double Whammy, Delirious, When You're Strange, and Down in Shadowland.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 15. Sep 2020) 7aPERFORMING ARTS / Film & Video / History & Criticism.2bisacsh1 aBuscemi, Steve08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCUP eBook Package 2017z978311065472108iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertCUP eBook-Package Pilot Project 2017z978311054330840uhttps://doi.org/10.7312/byrn1853440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780231851206423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780231851206.jpg  a978-3-11-054330-8  CUP eBook-Package Pilot Project 2017b2017  a978-3-11-065472-1  CUP eBook Package 2017b2017  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_CL_MUAR  aEBA_EBACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_ECL_MUAR  aEBA_EEBKALL  aEBA_ESSHALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_SSHALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA11SSHE  aPDA12STME  aPDA13ENGE  aPDA17SSHEE  aPDA5EBK